<!-- 话题详情页面 -->
<view class="page-container">
  <!-- 固定导航栏 -->
  <view class="fixed-navbar">
    <navigation-bar 
      title="话题详情" 
      background="#ffffff" 
      color="#000000" 
      back="{{true}}"
      home-button="{{false}}"
      left-logo="{{false}}"
      show-title="{{true}}"
    ></navigation-bar>
  </view>

  <!-- 页面内容区域 -->
  <view class="page-content">
    <!-- 话题头部信息 -->
    <view class="topic-header">
      <text class="topic-title">AI对创意产业的影响</text>
      <view class="topic-meta">
        <text class="participants">1.2k 人参与讨论</text>
        <text class="topic-tag">火热讨论中</text>
      </view>
      <text class="topic-desc">
        AI技术的飞速发展正以前所未有的速度重塑创意产业。从辅助绘画到自动生成文本，它究竟是创作者的得力助手，还是潜在的职业威胁？让我们一起探讨。
      </text>
    </view>

    <!-- 投票统计 -->
    <view class="vote-section">
      <view class="vote-card">
        <view class="vote-header">
          <view class="vote-option">
            <text class="option-label">支持 (正方)</text>
            <text class="option-percent">65%</text>
          </view>
          <view class="vote-option">
            <text class="option-label">反对 (反方)</text>
            <text class="option-percent">35%</text>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class="vote-bar">
          <view class="vote-progress support" style="width: 65%;"></view>
          <view class="vote-progress oppose" style="width: 35%;"></view>
          <view class="vote-divider"></view>
        </view>
        <view class="vote-buttons">
          <button class="vote-btn support-btn">
            <text class="vote-icon">👍</text>
            <text class="vote-text">支持观点</text>
          </button>
          <button class="vote-btn oppose-btn">
            <text class="vote-icon">👎</text>
            <text class="vote-text">反对观点</text>
          </button>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <!-- 评论导航 -->
    <view class="comment-nav">
      <view class="nav-item active">
        <text class="nav-text">精选评论</text>
      </view>
      <view class="nav-item">
        <text class="nav-text">全部评论</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <!-- 评论列表 -->
    <view class="comment-section">
      <!-- 评论1 -->
      <view class="comment-card">
        <view class="comment-header">
          <view class="user-info">
            <image class="avatar" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDdSFSAb_2Nom-QtDHpM1MlMajXDmF7_faxE1KVJfwlx_1pmAIzhku44oyZC7_hNAMmbkfrX32VXuEs-72mjr0fhpp-keD1L8moqnSmWjuXfpzGKN_Amak3930YmusJkljjqi_GpY5StSdbuOkBOuSi1svp-pclUvoYsAHBsVnGldcVXHlQjrMzAjp_v9S1g3fNqA10nIho-7Eg677DldCG5JnfKjlDKUJV52WVnPqrRF_W9wsPJWleahqJVTB8rocdzSTQYBA-Nfs" />
            <view class="user-details">
              <view class="username-row">
                <text class="username">陈林</text>
                <text class="user-badge">Top Contributor</text>
              </view>
              <text class="comment-info">2小时前 · 广东</text>
            </view>
          </view>
          <view class="more-btn" bindtap="showBottomSheet">
            <text class="more-icon">⋯</text>
          </view>
        </view>
        <text class="comment-content">
          AI作为一种工具确实能极大提高初稿的产出效率，但真正的创意核心在于人类的情感共鸣。它能取代重复性劳动，却无法取代艺术家的灵魂。
        </text>
        <view class="comment-actions">
          <view class="action-btn">
            <text class="action-icon">👍</text>
            <text class="action-count">428</text>
          </view>
          <view class="action-btn">
            <text class="action-icon">💬</text>
            <text class="action-count">12</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>

      <!-- 评论2 -->
      <view class="comment-card">
        <view class="comment-header">
          <view class="user-info">
            <image class="avatar" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDT5nK_pDK-_tGtL0_qIoav5pe-NnBkke6kdG4TOFKreiRXsE8Ur9A8ayhNNZekorzO7ErPBwoczaUj2RBa2CTEmJ5zN3Q9T0TgBV7H_DYmK446ljF1xZ0rbCfKz1VoI-j6MR-jLjXWWsSedlDWDjRe1RqFmlnenjJSaLVC088Z1XYjoHMARqhwP24SUw9YiWhGA5jfH6TvnpyBSyD32_Kva2RUQonIcAJwnoSGSeTD5lGCfpXCj2Lp9oGJ9ZmzILwJmmi7XNDiq0k" />
            <view class="user-details">
              <view class="username-row">
                <text class="username">林晓萌</text>
                <text class="user-badge">资深插画师</text>
              </view>
              <text class="comment-info">5小时前 · 上海</text>
            </view>
          </view>
          <view class="more-btn" bindtap="showBottomSheet">
            <text class="more-icon">⋯</text>
          </view>
        </view>
        <text class="comment-content">
          版权问题依然是最大的门槛。在没有完善的法律规范前，AI的快速普及对原创作者来说可能是一种巨大的不公平。
        </text>
        <view class="comment-actions">
          <view class="action-btn">
            <text class="action-icon">👍</text>
            <text class="action-count">156</text>
          </view>
          <view class="action-btn active">
            <text class="action-icon">💬</text>
            <text class="action-count">5</text>
          </view>
        </view>
        
        <!-- 子评论 -->
        <view class="sub-comments">
          <view class="sub-comment">
            <view class="sub-user-info">
              <text class="sub-username">张大伟</text>
              <text class="sub-time">3小时前</text>
            </view>
            <text class="sub-content">
              确实，现在的训练集很多都是未经授权抓取的，这确实是个法律灰色地带。
            </text>
          </view>
          <view class="sub-comment">
            <view class="sub-user-info">
              <text class="sub-username">创意先锋</text>
              <text class="sub-time">2小时前</text>
            </view>
            <text class="sub-content">
              不仅仅是版权，创作的溢价感也在消失。
            </text>
          </view>
          <view class="show-more">
            <text class="more-text">展开剩余 3 条回复</text>
            <text class="more-icon">↓</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>

      <!-- 评论3 -->
      <view class="comment-card">
        <view class="comment-header">
          <view class="user-info">
            <image class="avatar" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAHENWKG0vTQjfv-wTrUbUZj9FuBh5u46QDA65Z3JkTIj5gxWj9rQoeUcAwI0db5IfHi74sTp--sEtEOLgaiISrsW6fdk1bfdv8swm6xQpvB2CqiNoo8Vd_0npQucW-XdtG5o31Fhcb_bVZCREE85gK7CBHcRulALvl6sh4wXIDMaMhjuH6Wil7bQ5X2tc5nlCPZ52IdZbTsGjFod0PoYl5CfPwTXrcB8W3KG3q_MiYLskjbDKo_w6RfWqxjbWzjTbHe9ebv2KE82Y" />
            <view class="user-details">
              <view class="username-row">
                <text class="username">TechDaily</text>
              </view>
              <text class="comment-info">1天前 · 北京</text>
            </view>
          </view>
          <view class="more-btn" bindtap="showBottomSheet">
            <text class="more-icon">⋯</text>
          </view>
        </view>
        <text class="comment-content">
          我们应该关注的是如何让AI与人协作。未来可能不再是画师与画师的竞争，而是掌握了AI工具的人与未掌握AI工具的人之间的竞争。
        </text>
        <view class="comment-actions">
          <view class="action-btn">
            <text class="action-icon">👍</text>
            <text class="action-count">89</text>
          </view>
          <view class="action-btn">
            <text class="action-icon">💬</text>
            <text class="action-count">3</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <!-- 底部输入框 -->
    <view class="input-section">
      <view class="input-container">
        <input class="comment-input" placeholder="写下你的看法..." />
        <view class="input-actions">
          <text class="input-icon">🖼️</text>
          <text class="input-icon">@</text>
        </view>
        <button class="send-btn">
          <text class="send-icon">➤</text>
        </button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- 底部导航栏 -->
  <bottom-nav 
    wx:if="{{true}}"
    current="{{currentTab}}" 
    bind:change="onTabChange"
  />

  <!-- 底部菜单栏遮罩 -->
  <view class="bottom-sheet-overlay {{showBottomSheet ? 'active' : ''}}" bindtap="closeBottomSheet">
    <view class="bottom-sheet {{showBottomSheet ? 'active' : ''}}" catchtap="">
      <view class="sheet-item" bindtap="onReportContent">
        <text class="sheet-icon">🚩</text>
        <text class="sheet-text">举报内容</text>
      </view>
      <view class="sheet-item" bindtap="onBlockUser">
        <text class="sheet-icon">🚫</text>
        <text class="sheet-text">拉黑用户</text>
      </view>
      <view class="sheet-item" bindtap="onSharePost">
        <text class="sheet-icon">📤</text>
        <text class="sheet-text">分享帖子</text>
      </view>
      <view class="sheet-item" bindtap="onCopyLink">
        <text class="sheet-icon">🔗</text>
        <text class="sheet-text">复制链接</text>
      </view>
      <view class="sheet-cancel" bindtap="closeBottomSheet">
        <text class="cancel-text">取消</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>